Step 1. Check The Containers

docker container ps



Step 2. Add the Prometheus Data Source in Grafana 

Login Grafana Console -> Default username and password is admin -> Set new password -> Connections -> Data sources -> Add data source -> Select The Loki -> 
Scroll Down Connection -> URL *(http://EC2-Public-IP:3100/) -> Scroll Down Save & test 



Step 3. Create The Dashboard in Grafana

Dashboards -> Create dashboard -> Add visualization -> Select data source(Select The loki) -> Click On Code



Step 4.  Check The Application Access Logs

Metrics browser -> Select Job(Select The apache) -> filename(Select The /var/log/access.log)



Step 5.  Check The Application Error Logs

Metrics browser -> Select Job(Select The apache) -> filename(Select The /var/log/error.log)
